verbose_text: In conclusion, the 3D culture of hiPSC derived NCCs promotes both the expression of corneal keratocyte specific genes and also the deposition of Keratocan in extracellular matrix suggesting that these cells can be induced to adopt a keratocyte fate in vitro.
evidence: 3D culture of hiPSC-derived NCCs promotes both the expression of corneal keratocyte-specific genes and also the deposition of Keratocan
